Notes: UW-EC leads 22-21, UWL ends first half on 7-0 run...UWL starts 2nd half on
11-2 run...UWL starts fourth quarter on 14-2 run...Clemment (UWL) ties
career-high with 17 points (also 17 vs. UW-EC earlier this season)...UWL's 1st
regular-season sweep of UW-EC since 1986-87...UWL outrebounds UW-EC, 41-26.
